Title: Explicit gauge invariant quantization of the Schwinger model on a circle
  in the functional Schr\"odinger representation
Authors: Joakim Hallin, Per Liljenberg
Comments: 20 pages, standard latex (epsf used)
Report-no: Goteborg ITP 95-29
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D54 (1996) 1723-1735
\\
  We solve the Schwinger model on a circle by first finding the explicit
groundstate functional(s). Having done this, we give the structure of the
Hilbert space and derive bosonization formulae in this formalism.
